  dialogue:
  - "Hazel needs help, huh? I guess I\u2019m going to the Earth Kingdom today. It
    shouldn\u2019t take long to get there. Excuse me! I'm just letting you know I'll
    be out for the day "
  - "Oh... that\u2019s unfortunate. Lucien wanted to study for your politics class
    today..."
  - 'Her letter made it sound urgent; Lucien can wait until tomorrow. '
  - Let us go see him, perhaps he can make you reconsider!
  - I don't think that is necessary, I'm just going to see my friend
  - Unfortunately I must insist princess. Otherwise we may have to fight
